- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is also likely as the paper presents designs relevant to TMR architectures. 
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems) is relevant as the paper discusses fault tolerance in systems that are subject to environmental conditions. 
- cs.EM (Electromagnetics) is relevant as the paper mentions radiation phenomena as a fault-inducing environment. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely as the paper focuses on hardware design, but it is still possible that software is used in conjunction with the TMR scheme.
